# STATUS — aa v2 /code-write workflow

**Last updated:** 2026-04-23
**Current phase:** 7/7 — review-stack COMPLETE; ready to ship with documented gaps.

## TL;DR

All 7 phases of `/code-write` have run end-to-end on 5 feature slugs (config-store,
machine-lifecycle, docker-images, docker-up, test-harness). `go test ./...` is
green across every package (unit + integration + e2e). Three e2e journey tests
are explicitly skipped pending hand-crafted HTTP snapshot fixtures.

